nce%20for%20the%20Kremlin%20leader%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bno%20limits%26quot%3B%20friendship%20with%20Beijing%20that%20has%20enabled%20Moscow%20to%20weather%20unprecedented%20sanctions%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20to%20try%20to%20wreck%20Russia's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Shoigu%2C%20Belousov%20arrives%20at%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%20with%20no%20military%20background.%20With%20Ukraine%20starting%20to%20receive%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20new%20military%20aid%20from%20its%20US%20and%20European%20allies%2C%20Russia%20faces%20the%20challenge%20of%20maximizing%20the%20impact%20of%20its%20own%20defense%20spending%2C%20which%20is%20surging%20to%20historically%20high%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9g4fgg68_putin-russia-war_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20spending%20on%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%20and%20Russia's%20security%20sector%20is%20approaching%206.7%25%20of%20gross%20domestic%20product%2C%20nearing%20levels%20reached%20by%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20Kremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20said%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Interfax%20news%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20spending%20levels%20aren't%20yet%20%26quot%3Bcritical%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20chose%20Belousov%20because%20of%20the%20need%20for%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20competitiveness%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%2C%20Peskov%20said%2C%20Interfax%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBelousov's%20appointment%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20Russian%20economy%20is%20being%20transformed%20into%20a%20war%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andrei%20Kolesnikov%2C%20a%20senior%20fe