o%20make%20a%20big%20issue%20out%20of%20it%2C%20it%20means%20they%20are%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Owaisi%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20incident%20yet%2C%20but%20shared%20the%20viral%20video%20on%20his%20Twitter%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20candidate%20has%20alleged%20discrepancies%20in%20voters'%20list.%20%26quot%3BThe%20police%20personnel%20seem%20very%20dull%2C%20they%20are%20not%20active.%20They%20are%20not%20checking%20anything.%20Senior%20citizen%20voters%20are%20coming%20here%2C%20but%20their%20names%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20videos%20are%20playing%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20polarised%20contest%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20seat%20and%20a%20family%20stronghold%20of%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%2C%20Ms%20Madhavi%20Latha%20had%20said%20she%20was%20hopeful%20of%20the%20support%20of%20Muslim%20voters%20too%20because%20the%20BJP%20has%20spoken%20about%20triple%20talaq%20and%20jobs%20for%20Muslim%20youngsters.%20The%20viral%20videos%20and%20the%20row%20surrounding%20them%20are%20likely%20to%20hit%20her%20outreach%20to%20minority%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715588340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5k48mud_madhavi-latha-grab_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhavi-latha-asaduddin-owaisi-2024-lok-sabha-election-bjp-candidate-asks-muslim-women-to-show-face-for-id-check-sparks-row-5652298%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kompella%20Madhavi%20Latha%2C%20BJP's%20firebrand%20candidate%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20is%20set%20to%20face%20a%20police%20case%20after%20a%20video%20showed%20her%20asking%20burqa-clad%20Muslim%20women%20at%20a%20polling%20booth%20to%20reveal%20their%20faces%20so%20that%20she%20can%20match%20them%20with%20photos%20on%20voter%20ID%20cards%22%2C%22author%22%