mit-shah-arvind-kejriwal-2024-lok-sabha-election-fighting-22-seats-promising-free-power-across-india-amit-shah-mocks-aap-5650934%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20has%20made%20various%20statements%2C%20one%20among%20which%20is%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20quit%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20next%20year%20-%20his%2075th%20birthday%20-%20to%20make%20way%20for%20his%20trusted%20lieutenant%2C%20Amit%20Shah.%20Another%20frill%20to%20that%20story%20is%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20will%20be%20removed%20within%20two%20months%20of%20the%20BJP's%20Lok%20Sabha%20victory%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20becoming%20a%20challenger%20to%20Shah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoll%20Predictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo.%20Kejriwal%20claims%20that%20psephologists%20and%20the%20'%3Cem%3Esatta%20bazar%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(the%20betting%20market)%20are%20pegging%20BJP's%20tally%20at%20230%20-%20far%20more%20than%20Rahul%20or%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20estimations%20of%20150-180.%20If%20Kejriwal's%20calculation%2C%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20miss%20the%20halfway%20mark%2C%20ultimately%20proves%20to%20be%20correct%2C%20what%20is%20the%20logic%20behind%20his%20claim%20that%20after%20elections%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20drive%20the%20nation%20towards%20a%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Leader%20'%20model%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree.%20Kejriwal%20has%20long%20been%20a%20master%20of%20disruption%20and%20obfuscation.%20Rhetoric%20plays%20a%20role%20during%20campaigns%2C%20but%20political%20pundits%20are%20taking%20neither%20him%20nor%20the%20Congress%20siblings%20seriously%20in%20terms%20of%20poll%20predictions.%20The%20ground%20current%20at%20present%20does%20not%20suggest%20a%20downturn%20in%20the%20fortunes%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour.%20The%20AAP%20has%20zero%20seats%20in%20the%20outgoing%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20but%20the%20decibel%20of%20its%20leader%20is%20arguably%20higher%20than%20the%20pitch%20of%20all%20other%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20put%20together.%20In%20the%2022%20seats%20it%20is%20contesting%2C%20the%20AAP%20challenges%20the%20BJP%20in%20nine%2C%20while%20in%20the%20remaining%2013%20in%20Punjab%2C%20it%20is%20up%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20defending%20eight%20of%20these%20seats.%20Confident%20that%20he%20can%20handle%20its%20INDIA%20ally%2C%20Kejriwal%20is%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20spoiler%20for%20the%20BJP.%20He%20is%20seeking%20to%20puncture%20the%20party's%20poll%20pitch%2C%20'Modi%20Ki%20Guarantee'%2C%20through%20conspiracy%20theories%20about%20its%20succession%20plans%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20BJP%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20summarily%20dismissed%20such%20statements%20as%20fantasy%20and%20chided%20Kejriwal%20about%20his%20own%20succession%20plans%20-%20or%20the%20lack%20thereof%20-%20which%20compelled%20him%20to%20cling%20to%20chief%20ministership%20even%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKejriwal's%20Guarantees%20-%20INDIA's%20Too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive.%20Kejriwal%20has%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-promises-free-electricity-healthcare-if-aap-wins-2024-polls-5645253%5C%22%3Eten-point%20agenda%20of%20his%20own%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20he%20calls%20'Kejriwal%20Ki%20Guarantee'%2C%20and%20has%20%3Cem%3Esuo%20motu%3C%2Fem%3E%20declared%20that%20it%20will%20be%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20agenda%20too%20if%20it%20forms%20a%20government.%20That%20he%20did%20not%20consider%20or%20consult%20with%20his%20allies%20before%20making%20this%20announcement%20is%20a%20different%20matter.%20So%20much%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Bautocracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix.%20A%20master%20in%20stitching%20appealing%20narratives%2C%20Kejriwal%20emerged%20as%20a%20mass%20leader%20during%20the%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20movement%20in%202012%2C%20which%20ultimately%2C%20according%20to%20many%2C%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20Congress's%20undoing.%20The%20party%20is%20now%20the%20AAP's%20ally%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20The%20list%20of%20contradictions%20is%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-cm-arvind-kejriwal-out-on-bail-how-effective-will-his-aggressive-campaigning-be-5644147%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Kejriwal%20Out%20On%20Bail%3A%20How%20Effective%20Will%20His%20Intense%20Campaigning%20Be%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven.%20The%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20release%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20a%2021-day%20interim%20bail%20to%20enable%20him%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20election%20campaign%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%20For%20one%2C%20he%20did%20not%20seek%20bail%20but%20challenged%20the%20legality%20of%20his%20arrest.%20That%20matter%20awaits%20adjudication.%20The%20top%20court%20has%20placed%20restrictions%20on%20his%20functioning%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20has%20barred%20him%20from%20commenting%20on%20the%20case.%20This%2C%20apart%20from%20putting%20estoppels%20on%20his%20functioning%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20means%20he%20cannot%20go%20to%20the%20Secretariat%20or%20sign%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Religious%20Outreach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight.%20Kejriwal%20stole%20the%20Opposition's%20thunder%20as%20he%20walked%20out%20of%20Tihar%20jail%20after%2051%20days%20of%20incarceration.%20Invoking%20Lord%20Hanuman%2C%20he%20jumped%20into%20the%20ring%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20latter's%20own%20domain%2C%20Hindutva.%20Before%20embarking%20on%20his%20'Mission%202024'%2C%20he%C2%A0went%20to%20New%20Delhi's%20Hanuman%20Mandir%20along%20with%20his%20family%20and%20the%20AAP's%20top%20brass%2C%20and%20also%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20South%20Indian%20temple%20next%20door%20to%20offer%20prayers%20to%20Shani%2C%20the%20God%20of%20justice%20and%20retribution.%20Then%20he%20drove%20to%20the%20party%20headquarters%20to%20address%20what%20was%20purported%20to%20be%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20but%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20rally%20to%20celebrate%20Kejriwal's%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20the%20prominent%20presence%20of%20Mann%20in%20his%20entourage%20notwithstanding%2C%20Kejriwal%20did%20not%20pay%20obeisance%20at%20the%20Bangla%20Sahib%20Gurdwara%2C%20which%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20eighth%20Sikh%20Guru%2C%20Harkishan%20Dev%2C%20and%20is%20of%20the%2018th-century%20vintage.%20Of%20the%20total%20of%2022%20seats%20the%20AAP%20is%20in%20the%20fray%20for%2C%2013%2C%20or%2059%25%2C%20are%20in%20Punjab.%20That%20Kejriwal's%20religious%20outreach%20did%20not%20account%20for%20these%20voters%20-%20Sikhs%20not%20just%20in%20Punjab%20but%20also%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana%20-%20is%20odd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-have-to-go-back-to-jail-if-you-choose-aap-arvind-kejriwals-pitch-5647167%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Won't%20Have%20To%20Go%20Back%20To%20Jail%20If%20You%20Choose%20AAP%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Pitch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine.%20Kejriwal%20seems%20to%20have%20already%20breached%20the%20apex%20court's%20directive%20by%20asserting%20that%20he%20was%20implicated%20in%20a%20'false%20case'.%20The%20BJP's%20national%20spokesman%2C%20Sudhangshu%20Trivedi%2C%20was%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20that%20Kejriwal%20may%20have%20'violated%20a%20bail%20norm'.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20what%20view%20the%20court%20takes%20of%20this%20deviation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20notably%20while%20taking%20the%20unprecedented%20step%20of%20granting%20interim%20bail%20to%20a%20person%20who%20had%20not%20even%20applied%20for%20it%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20allowing%20Kejriwal%20to%20campaign%20for%2021%20days%20as%20his%20case%20would%20have%20taken%20time%20to%20conclude.%20Notably%2C%20Kejriwal's%20plea%20to%20grant%20him%20bail%20till%20June%204%2C%20the%20day%20results%20are%20to%20be%20declared%2C%20was%20declined%2C%20and%20he%20has%20to%20return%20to%20Tihar%20on%20June%202%2C%20a%20day%20after%20polling%20is%20over%20in%20Punjab.%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana%2C%20where%20the%20AAP%20is%20contesting%2014%20seats%20in%20total%20(only%20a%20single%20seat%20in%20Haryana)%2C%20vote%20on%20May%2025%2C%20while%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Assam%2C%20where%20it%20is%20contesting%20two%20seats%20each%2C%20voting%20is%20already%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Soren%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20ten.%20It'll%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20whether%20the%20Kejriwal%20precedent%20will%20now%20be%20cited%20by%20Hemant%20Soren%20too%2C%20the%20incarcerated%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jharkhand%20who%20is%20facing%20charges%20of%20corruption.%20Ten%20of%20the%20state's%2014%20seats%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20the%20fifth%2C%20sixth%20and%20seventh%20rounds%20of%20voting.%20Like%20Kejriwal%2C%20Soren%2C%20too%2C%20was%20an%20elected%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM).%20It%20was%20founded%20in%201972%2C%20four%20decades%20before%20AAP%20came%20into%20being.%20Unlike%20Kejriwal%20though%2C%20Soren%20did%20not%20avoid%20nine%20summonses%20from%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20-%20which%2C%20to%20be%20clear%2C%20is%20a%20grave%20offence%20in%20itself%2C%20and%20of%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20a%20negative%20view%20in%20Kejriwal's%20case.%20Soren%2C%20instead%2C%20surrendered%20and%20went%20to%20jail.%20He%20also%20quit%20his%20post%2C%20allowing%20Champai%20Soren%20to%20be%20Chief%20Minister.%20As%20for%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20JMM's%20allies%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20symbolically%20left%20a%20chair%20vacant%20for%20Hemant%20Soren%20too%20in%20their%20Delhi%20and%20Ranchi%20rallies.%20Will%20-%20and%20should%20-%20he%20be%20allowed%20to%20campaign%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715588280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1j4dmcak_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_11_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-arvind-kejriwals-release-a-catalogue-of-contradictions-5652178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20release%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20a%2021-day%20interim%20bail%20to%20enable%20him%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20election%20campaign%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%20For%20one%2C%20his%20plea%20did%20not%20seek%20bail%2C%20it%20had%20challenged%20the%20legality%20of%20his%20arrest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-arvind-kejriwals-release-a-catalogue-of-contradictions-5652178%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Legal%20Merit%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Junks%20Another%20Plea%20To%20Sack%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20snubbed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20the%20removal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Farvind-kejriwal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi%20following%20his%20arrest%20in%20March%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-scam%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20plea%20was%20filed