emocracy%20take%20its%20own%20course%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flet-democracy-take-its-own-course-court-dismisses-petition-against-arvind-kejriwal-5371982%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BLet%20Democracy%20Take%20Its%20Course%26quot%3B%3A%20Plea%20To%20Remove%20Kejriwal%20Rejected%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Saxena)%20doesn't%20need%20our%20guidance.%20We%20are%20nobody%20to%20advise%20him.%20He%20will%20do%20whatever%20he%20has%20to%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20acting%20Chief%20Justice%20Manmohan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20dismissed%20a%20similar%20plea%20back%20in%202019%2C%20when%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20facing%20prosecution%20in%20a%20criminal%20case.%20%26quot%3BProsecution%20is%20still%20going%20on.%20He%20may%20get%20acquitted.%20What%20will%20you%20do%20then%3F%20Come%20after%20he%20is%20convicted%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20Rajendra%20Menon%20said%20then%2C%20%26quot%3BNothing%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejiwal-leaves-jail-after-50-days-election-gamechanger-says-aap-5633876%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20Leaves%20Jail%20After%2050%20Days%2C%20Says%20%26quot%3BNeed%20To%20Fight%20Dictatorship%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20March%2021%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20roiled%20the%20AAP%20weeks%20before%20the%20election.%20The%20arresting%20agency%20-%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20-%20has%20claimed%20the%20(now%20scrapped)%20policy%20allowed%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20receive%20kickbacks%20for%20license%20allotment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20kickbacks%20amounted%20to%20Rs%20100%20cro