usy%20writing%20the%20goodbye%20mail%E2%80%9D%2C%C2%A0began%20with%20a%20greeting%20to%20the%C2%A0superiors.%C2%A0%26quot%3BHope%20you%20both%20are%20well%20and%20good%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0before%20quickly%20taking%20a%20different%20tone%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20we%C2%A0didn't%C2%A0meet%20today%20as%20you%20are%20not%20here-strange%2C%20but%20I%20DID%20guess%20and%20expected%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20then%C2%A0went%20on%20to%20voice%C2%A0her%20frustration%20with%20the%20managers'%C2%A0leadership%20styles%2C%20claiming%20that%20working%20with%20them%20was%20like%C2%A0%26quot%3Bgoing%20through%20the%203rd%20class%20torture.%26quot%3B%C2%A0The%20person%2C%20whose%20mail%20initials%20are%20BD%2C%C2%A0described%C2%A0the%20work%20environment%20as%C2%A0%26quot%3BHITLER'S%C2%A0RACE%26quot%3B%2C%C2%A0calling%C2%A0%3Cwbr%3Emanagers'%C2%A0behaviour%20unethical%20and%20unprofessional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%C2%A0at%20all%C2%A0pleasurable%20for%20me%20to%20work%20with%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0the%20email%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20went%20on%20to%20detail%20specific%20instances%20of%20being%20mistreated%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20like%20being%20asked%C2%A0to%C2%A0%26quot%3Bstay%20back%20after%20every%20team%20huddle-then%20shouting%20at%20me%2Fmailing%20me%2Ftagging%20me%2Fnagging%C2%A0me-no%C2%A0stone%20left%20unturned.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20detailed%20how%20the%20employee%C2%A0was%20addressed%C2%A0in%20team%20huddles%20as%C2%A0%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20are%20on%20their%20notice%20period%26quot%3B%C2%A0and%20subjected%C2%A0to%20rude%20and%20arrogant%20behaviour%2C%20with%20the%20managers%20talking%20to%20them%C2%A0%E2%80%9Crudely%2F%20arrogantly%2F%20yelling-unprofessionally%20and%20unethically%20%3Cem%3ETU%20ye%2FTU%20vo%2FTU%20ase%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20management%20would%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cshout%20and%20yell%E2%80%9D%C2%A0at%20the