%20leader's%20appointment%20of%20a%20civilian%20economist%20with%20no%20military%20experience%20as%20defense%20minister%20signals%20Putin%20expects%20the%20military-industrial%20complex%20to%20be%20a%20key%20pillar%20of%20Russia's%20wartime%20economy%20amid%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20suggests%20Putin%20may%20be%20preparing%20for%20a%20confrontation%20with%20NATO%20in%20the%20future%2C%20analysts%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iswresearch.org%2F2024%2F05%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment_12.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstitute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20a%20think%20tank%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20points%20to%20a%20long%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBelousov's%20appointment%20to%20the%20position%20of%20Russian%20Defense%20Minister%20is%20a%20significant%20development%20in%20Putin's%20efforts%20to%20set%20full%20economic%20conditions%20for%20a%20protracted%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223566fa2c-92a9-427a-9d08-a80ebb971bad%5C%22%3EDefense%20minister%20Belousov%20will%20be%20a%20'financial%20administrator'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBelousov's%20appointment%20to%20defense%20minister%20is%20unlikely%20to%20impact%20military%20operations%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValery%20Gerasimov%2C%20Russia's%20top%20general%20and%20chief%20of%20general%20staff%2C%20will%20remain%20in%20his%20position%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20directing%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20Mark%20Galeotti%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20London-based%20Mayak%20Intelligence%20consultancy%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-proposes-sacking-defence-minister-shoigu-parliament-says-2024-05-12%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gerasimov%20reports%20directly%20to%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20that%20cont