3E%20%5BHe%20was%20vulnerable%20in%20that%20matter.%20He%20was%20a%20good%20man%2C%20and%20good%20people%20are%20often%20affected%2C%20right%3F%20At%20times%2C%20he%20used%20to%20come%20to%20me%20and%20ask%2C%20'What%20should%20I%20do%2C%20sir%3F'%20So%20I%20used%20to%20tell%20him%2C%20'Bro%2C%20don't%20take%20it%20too%20seriously.%20I%20know%20because%20I%20have%20suffered%2C%20I%20am%20suffering%2C%20I%20am%20still%20suffering.%5D'%E2%80%9D%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%C2%A0died%20on%20June%2014%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EManoj%20Bajpayee%20also%20added%20how%20he%20had%20shared%20his%20approach%20to%20dealing%20with%20such%20articles%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fon-sushant-singh-rajputs-birth-anniversary-sister-shweta-singh-kirti-shares-special-note-4908527%5C%22%3ESushant%20Singh%20Rajput%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20actor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKuch%20ek%20log%20hai%20bhai%20%5BSushant%20Singh%20Rajput%5D%20jo%20log%2C%20jinki%20filmein%20chal%20rahi%20hai%2C%20jo%20power%20me%20hai%2C%20unko%20handle%2C%20mai%20to%20handle%20dusre%20treeke%20se%20karta%20hu.%20Mai%20to%20unke%20dosto%20ko%20bolta%20hu%20ki%20unka%20bolna%20ki%20aake%20marunga%20mai%20tujhe.%20Kyuki%20mai%20jaanta%20hu%20ki%20dosta%20jaake%20bolega%20ki%20Manoj%20keh%20raha%20tha%20ki%20tujhe%20maarega.%20Mai%20to%20bihari%20aadmi%2Cmai%20aise%20jhagda%20nahi%20krta%20hu%20kise%20se.%20Uske%20dost%20ko%20bolo%2C%20ya%20dost%20ke%20dost%20ko%20bolo.%20To%20dost%20jo%20hai%2C%20dost%20ko%20bolega%2C%20dost%20jaake%20usko%20bolega%2C%20ki%20Manoj%20tujhe%20maarega.%20To%20baat%20pahunch%20jaye%20yahi%20chahiye%20na%3F%20To%20hasta%20tha%2C%20Sushant%20bahut%20hasta%20tha%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%5BThere%20are%20some%20people%2C%20brother%2C%20whose%20films%20are%20doing%20well%2C%20who%20are%20in%20power%3B%20I%20handle%20them%20differently.%20I%20tell%20their%20friends%20that%20I'll%20come%20and%20beat%20you%20up.%20Because%20I%20know%20that%20if%20a%20friend%20goes%20and%20says%20that%20Manoj%20said%20he'll%20beat%20you%20up%2C%20they'll%20get%20scared.%20I%20am%20a%20Bihari%20man%3B%20I%20don't%20pick%20fights%20with%20anyone%20like%20that.%20Tell%20their%20friends%2C%20or%20their%20friends'%20friends.%20So%2C%20the%20friend%20will%20tell%20the%20friend%20to%20tell%20them%20that%20Manoj%20will%20beat%20you%20up.%20That's%20all%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20communicated%2C%20right%3F%20So%2C%20Sushant%20used%20to%20laugh%3B%20he%20laughed%20a%20lot.%5D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThen%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%20quoted%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20reply%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESir%20yeh%20aap%20hi%20karte%20sakte%20ho.%20Mai%20nahi%20kar%20skata.%20Mai%20kaise%20karu%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%5BSir%2C%20only%20you%20can%20do%20this.%20I%20can't.%20How%20can%20I%20do%20it%3F%5D%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20he%20used%20to%20get%20troubled%20by%20those%20blind%20articles%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manoj%20mentioned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20about%20his%20bond%20with%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBahut%20sensitive%20aur%20bahut%20hi%20intelligent%20aadmi%20tha.%20Aur%20mai%20jo%20mutton%20bna%20ke%20khilata%20tha%20set%20pe%20uska%20deewana%20tha%2C%20kyuki%20basically%20to%20bihari%20tha%20vo.%20To%20jo%20meat%20bhaat%20hum%20log%20khaate%20the%2C%20mai%20banata%20tha%2C%20aur%20kayi%20baar%20khaya%20usne%20auer%20bolta%20bhi%20rehta%20tha%20ki%20Manoj%20bhai%20aapke%20ghar%20aake%20khana%20hai.%20Maine%20(bola)%20jaise%20hi%20banauga%2C%20mai%20tujhe%20bulaunga.%20That%20was%20our%20last%20talk.%20And%20theek%20uske%2010%20din%20ke%20baad%2C%20he%20passed%20away%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%5BHe%20was%20a%20sensitive%20and%20intelligent%20person.%20And%2C%20he%20used%20to%20love%20the%20mutton%20dish%20I%C2%A0%20cooked%20on%20the%20set%20because%20he%20was%20basically%20from%20Bihar.%20So%2C%20the%20meat%20and%20rice%20that%20we%20used%20to%20eat%2C%20I%20used%20to%20cook%2C%20and%20many%20times%20he%20would%20eat%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Manoj%20bhai%2C%20I%20want%20to%20come%20to%20your%20house%20and%20eat.'%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98As%20soon%20as%20I%20make%20it%2C%20I%20will%20call%20you.'%20That%20was%20our%20last%20conversation.%20And%20exactly%2010%20days%20later%2C%20he%20passed%20away.%5D%20God%20bless%20his%20soul.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EManoj%20Bajpayee%20also%20shared%20his%20reaction%20to%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20death.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%2C%20like%20everyone%2C%20who%20was%20very%20close%20to%20him%20or%20around%20him%2C%20shocked%2C%20shattered.%20I%20was%20one%20of%20them.%20I%20just%20could%20not%20believe%20it.%C2%A0Abhi%20bhi%2C%20jaise%20mai%20believe%20nahi%20kar%20paata%20hu%20jaise%20do%20logo%20ki%20mrityu%20ko%20lekar%20ke.%20Ek%20Sushant%20ki%2C%20ek%20Irrfan%20(Khan)%20ki.%C2%A0It%20was%20too%20early.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20them%20going%20away.%20Kisi%20ki%20age%20ho%20jaati%20hai%20to%20aap%20ussey%20samjhota%20kar%20lete%20ho.%20Lekin%20abhi%20bas%20thrive%20kar%20rahe%20the%20yeh%20log.%C2%A0They%20were%20thriving%2C%20they%20were%20doing%20good%20work.%C2%A0Vaqt%20aa%20gya%20tha%20in%20logo%20ka.%C2%A0Irrfan%20has%20been%20doing%20so%20well%2C%20nationally%2C%20and%20internationally.%C2%A0Inke%20nahi%20hone%20ka%20abhi%20tak%20ehsaas%20ho%20nahi%20paya.%C2%A0%5BEven%20now%2C%20I%20can't%20believe%20it.%20I%20can't%20believe%20the%20deaths%20of%20two%20people.%20One%20is%20Sushant's%20and%20the%20other%20is%20Irrfan%20Khan's.%20It%20was%20too%20early.%20It's%20difficult%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20them%20going%20away.%20When%20someone%20gets%20older%2C%20you%20can%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20it.%20But%20they%20were%20just%20thriving.%20They%20were%20doing%20good%20work.%20It%20was%20their%20time.%20Irrfan%20has%20been%20doing%20so%20well%2C%20nationally%20and%20internationally.%20I%20still%20can't%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20their%20absence.%5D%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Factor-irrfan-khan-dies-in-mumbai-at-53-2220189%5C%22%3EIrrfan%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2053%C2%A0in%20Mumbai's%20Kokilaben%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%20Hospital.%20He%C2%A0was%20being%20treated%20for%20a%20colon%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715582280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1ifskfao_vicky-_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-on-how-blind-articles-affected-sushant-singh-rajput-5651278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%C2%A0died%20on%20June%2014%2C%202020%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-on-how-blind-articles-affected-sushant-singh-rajput-5651278%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-on-how-blind-articles-affected-sushant-singh-rajput-5651278%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-on-how-blind-articles-affected-sushant-singh-rajput-5651278%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEarning%20A%20400-Crore%20Profit...%26quot%3B%3A%20Sehwag's%20Fiery%20Take%20On%20Rahul-Goenka%20Saga%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELucknow%20Super%20Giants%20found%20themselves%20in%20the%20headlines%20during%20IPL%202024%20following%20owner%20Sanjiv%20Goenka's%20fiery%20chat%20with%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20their%20huge%20loss%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad.%20LSG