Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20is%20a%20key%20state%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20With%20its%20contingent%20of%2040%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Bihar%20stands%20as%20the%20fourth-largest%20contributor%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20recent%20political%20landscape%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20tectonic%20shifts%2C%20with%20the%20most%20significant%20being%20the%20return%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20JD(U)%20party%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBihar%20has%20infused%20this%20resolve%20with%20new%20colours.%20It%20has%20given%20it%20new%20strength.%20The%20atmosphere%20across%20the%20country%20is%20mirrored%20in%20Bihar%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20JD(U)%20had%20formed%20a%20formidable%20alliance%2C%20contesting%2017%20seats%20each%2C%20while%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%20had%20its%20share%20of%20six%20constituencies.%20The%20BJP-JDU%20combine%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20all%20their%20designated%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20clinched%20victory%20in%20Kishanganj%2C%20leaving%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20empty-handed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715579700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F619u0fuo_pm-modi-langar-_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-wearing-turban-pm-modi-serves-langar-at-historic-patna-gurdwara-5651226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wearing%20a%20turban%20and%20holding%20a%20pot%20of%20kheer%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20served%20langar%2C%20a%20communal%20meal%2C%20to%20devotees%20at%20the%20Takhat%20Sri%20Harimandir%20Ji%20Patna%20Sahib%20Gurdwara%20in%20Bihar's%20capital%20Patna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-wearing-turban-pm-modi-serves-langar-at-historic-patna-gurdwara-5