%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV.%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20already%20won%20two%20elections%20with%20full%20majority%2C%20and%20if%20changing%20the%20Constitution%20was%20his%20agenda%2C%20he%20could%20have%20easily%20done%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20ji%20became%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20twice.%20He%20had%20a%20clear%20mandate%20both%20times.%20So%20if%20the%20BJP%20government%20wanted%20to%20change%20the%20constitution%2C%20or%20remove%20reservation%2C%20who%20could%20have%20stopped%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20Amit%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20instead%20used%20our%20majority%20to%20finish%20Article%20370%2C%20triple%20talaq%2C%20to%20build%20Ram%20temple%2C%20to%20conduct%20a%20surgical%20strike%2C%20to%20land%20Chandrayaan%2C%20to%20save%20130%20crores%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20to%20provide%2060%20crore%20people%20toilet%2C%20cooking%20gas%2C%20home%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20power%20supply%2C%20free%20ration%2C%20and%20health%20costs%20up%20to%205%20lakh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah's%20remarks%20come%20after%20claims%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20%26quot%3Btear%20up%20and%20throw%20away%26quot%3B%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20retains%20power.%20Some%20other%20Congress%20functionaries%20had%20expressed%20apprehensions%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20drop%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bsecularism%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Preamble%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20was%20spreading%20lies%20to%20mislead%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20wants%20to%20mislead%20the%20country.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20country%20know%20this.%20Either%20he%20is%20delusional%20or%20is%20spreading%20delusion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Constitution%20has%20ensured%20opportunities%20for%20everyon