%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20voted%20to%20unionize%20in%20June%202022%20and%20have%20been%20negotiating%20with%20Apple's%20management%20since%20January%202023.%20Their%20past%20proposals%20for%20Apple%20have%20included%20more%20time%20off%20and%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-workers-union-in-towson-fighting-for-tipping-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etipping%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Saturday's%20statement%20did%20not%20include%20information%20about%20what%20specifics%20the%20union%20is%20currently%20negotiating%20over%20with%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20date%20has%20been%20set%20for%20the%20strike%2C%20the%20union%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employees%20at%20the%20Towson%20store%20organized%20as%20the%20Coalition%20of%20Organized%20Retail%20Employees%20in%202022%20when%20they%20voted%20to%20be%20represented%20by%20the%20International%20Association%20of%20Machinists%20%26amp%3B%20Aerospace%20Workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20100%20Towson%20Apple%20store%20employees%20belong%20to%20the%20union%2C%20which%20also%20represents%20600%2C000%20workers%20from%20companies%20like%20Boeing%2C%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20and%20United%20Airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20deeply%20value%20our%20team%20members%20and%20we're%20proud%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20industry%20leading%20compensation%20and%20exceptional%20benefits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20company%20is%20facing%20labor-related%20issues%20at%20the%20Maryland%20store%20and%20elsewhere.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20National%20Labor%20Relations%20Board%20filed%20a%20complaint%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Towson%20workers%2C%20which%20alleged%20Apple%20%3C