Some%20businesses%20prefer%20to%20use%20a%20vendor%20like%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform%20to%20avoid%20managing%20their%20own%20data%20centers%20or%20server%20farms.%3Cp%3EPau%20Barrena%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-cookie-delay-underscores-its-ad-industry-dominance-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Ads%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20businesses%20build%20and%20optimize%20their%20online%20presence%20without%20necessarily%20becoming%20computing%20or%20advertising%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Google%20offers%20dozens%20of%20products%20through%20its%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform%20in%20categories%20that%20include%20computing%2C%20storage%2C%20databases%2C%20operations%2C%20developer%20tools%2C%20data%20analytics%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20appealing%20to%20many%20businesses%20because%20it%20offers%20scalability%20and%20reach%20without%20the%20need%20to%20own%20or%20maintain%20their%20own%20data%20centers%20or%20server%20farms.%20It%20also%20offloads%20the%20headaches%20and%20responsibility%20for%20security%20and%20compliance%20from%20businesses%2C%20since%20Google%20handles%20all%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20wealth%20of%20options%20within%20the%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform.%20GCP's%20App%20Engine%20lets%20you%20build%20and%20host%20applications%20on%20the%20same%20systems%20where%20Google's%20own%20applications%20live%2C%20with%20the%20advantages%20of%20fast%20development%20and%20deployment%2C%20easy%20scalability%2C%20and%20simple%20administration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20Google's%20storage%20offerings%20is%20its%20Cloud%20Storage%20service%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20store%20and%20access%20your%20data%20on%20Google's%20infrastructure.%20It%20combines%20scalability%20with%20Google's%20integrated%20security%20and%20sharing.%20There%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20networking%20tools%2C%20including%20Cloud%20CDN%2C%20Cloud%20DNS%2C%20Cloud%20Firewall%2C%20Cloud%20VPN%2C%20and%20Virtual%20Private%20Cloud%20%E2%80%94%20a%20completely%20secure%20and%20private%20network%20topology%20that%20delivers%20a%20secure%20environment%20for%20your%20deployments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20need%20data%20analytics%2C%20GCP%20offers%20BigQuery%2C%20a%20data%20analysis%20service%20that%20lets%20businesses%20analyze%20big%20data%20that%20measures%20in%20the%20hundreds%20of%20terabytes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d91c546-3b45-417e-bd7a-9ec4f4573528%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20difference%20between%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform%20and%20Google%20Cloud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20those%20offerings%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20confuse%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform%20with%20Google%20Cloud%20%E2%80%94%20they%20have%20deceptively%20similar%20names%2C%20and%20Google%20itself%20sometimes%20uses%20the%20terms%20interchangeably.%20That%20said%2C%20one%20is%20not%20always%20just%20a%20shorthand%20for%20the%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Google%20Cloud%20represents%20the%20full%20suite%20of%20public%20cloud%20computing%20services%20offered%20by%20the%20search%20giant%2C%20of%20which%20GCP%20is%20just%20one%20component.%20Google%20Cloud%2C%20for%20example%2C%20includes%20Google%20Workspace%20(the%20suite%20of%20productivity%20tools%20like%20Google%20Docs%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-formulas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Sheets%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20formerly%20known%20as%20G%20Suite%20and%20Google%20Apps).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3bde5a7-7607-457f-8c58-e6018f79a03a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform%20free%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20office%20workers%20huddle%20near%20a%20computer%20on%20a%20desk.%5C%22%20cha