s%20a%20toddler%2C%20I%20couldn't%20stand%20long%20enough%20to%20cook%20dinner%2C%20let%20alone%20bake.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20many%20hobbies%20this%20disease%20stole%20from%20me%20as%20my%20body%20declined%20and%20my%20search%20for%20a%20diagnosis%20grew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlour.%20Sugar.%20Baking%20powder.%20Vanilla%20extract.%20Butter.%20Eggs.%20By%20the%20time%20I'd%20collected%20all%20the%20ingredients%20on%20the%20counter%2C%20my%20legs%20were%20devoid%20of%20energy.%20I%20stirred%20until%20my%20arm%20muscles%20throbbed%20%E2%80%94%20often%2C%20it%20wasn't%20long%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%2C%20I'd%20push%20on%20anyway%2C%20determined%20to%20hang%20on%20to%20this%20one%20piece%20of%20myself%20so%20that%20I%20wasn't%20defined%20by%20this%20disease.%20But%20after%20sifting%2C%20pouring%2C%20mixing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20standing%20%E2%80%94%20weakness%20and%20pain%20would%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20legs%20begged%20for%20rest%2C%20I'd%20slowly%20sink%20downward%20into%20a%20sitting%20position%20until%20I%20reached%20the%20kitchen%20floor.%20There%2C%20I%20cried%2C%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20who%20I%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20hung%20up%20my%20apron%20as%20I%20waited%20for%20a%20diagnosis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20I%20was%20once%20a%20baker%2C%26quot%3B%20I'd%20tell%20myself.%20But%20now%2C%20I%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristina-applegate-what-to-expect-when-diagnosed-with-multiple-sclerosis-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronically%20ill%3C%2Fa%3E%20mother%20struggling%20to%20survive%2C%20and%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20recognize%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20the%20kitchen%20was%20a%20reminder%20that%20I%20was%20living%20with%20a%20debilitating%20yet%20mysterious%20disease.%20When%20cooking%2C%20I'd%20lean%20on%20the%20counter%20to%20relieve%20some%20of%20the%20weight%20my%20body%20was%20supporting%2C%20but%20that%20only%20helped%20for%20so%20long.%20I'd%20prepare%20me