lighar%20opened%20its%20gates%20to%20its%20first%20guests.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20homestay%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20happy%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESteeped%20in%20tradition%20and%20sustainability%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalighar%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20homestay%20that%20smells%20of%20customs%20and%20traditions%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20luxury%20and%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20homestay%20gives%20the%20guests%20is%20an%20authentic%20escape%20from%20their%20city%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKabir%20shares%20that%20growing%20up%2C%20he%20noticed%20how%20the%20houses%20in%20the%20area%20were%20being%20modernised.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20old-school%20mud%20homes%20with%20sloping%20bamboo%20roofs%2C%20which%20were%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20area%2C%20were%20all%20gone.%20In%20losing%20our%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20losing%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20preserve%20the%20traditional%20culture%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20traditional%20technique%20called%20Irka%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CEssentially%2C%20what%20the%20technique%20involves%20is%20using%20bamboo%2C%20wood%20and%20mud%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20The%20mud%2C%20mixed%20with%20dung%20and%20straw%2C%20is%20plastered%20on%20a%20wooden%20frame%20woven%20with%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Kabir%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20made%20mud%20bricks%20which%20are%20baked%20in%20the%20sun.%20We%20used%20the%20land%20from%20our%20own%20property%20which%20helped%20us%20reduce%20our%20carbon%20footprint.%20We%20were%20really%20conscious%20of%20the%20impact%20we%20have%20on%20the%20nature%20around%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Ahana%20also%20points%20out%2