nge%20and%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20green%20revolution%2C%20our%20grandparents%20were%20growing%20millets%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%2C%20ragi%2C%20and%20bajra%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20their%20farms%2C%20which%20require%20less%20water%20and%20are%20resilient%20to%20climate%20change.%20The%20advent%20of%20the%20green%20revolution%20caused%20a%20shift%20to%20paddy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shashidhar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabu%20chimes%20in%2C%20as%20Arun%20and%20his%20family%20too%2C%20share%20a%20similar%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20no%20secret%20that%20farmers%20in%20the%20delta%20districts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20including%20Trichy%2C%20have%20experienced%20years%20of%20poor%20paddy%20yields%20due%20to%20insufficient%20water%20for%20irrigation%2C%20forcing%20many%20to%20seek%20alternative%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20of%20discussion%20before%20they%20quit%20their%20jobs%20led%20them%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20cultivating%20millets%20on%20their%20existing%20land%20in%20Trichy%20and%20Hyderabad.%20Shashidhar%20even%20purchased%20an%20additional%2040%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20started%20growing%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20ragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20seasonal%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20growing%20millets%20was%20one%20part%20of%20the%20vision%2C%20the%20other%20part%20was%20drawn%20from%20their%20experiences.%20They%20noticed%20a%20shift%20towards%20healthy%2C%20vegan%20food%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20dietary%20requirements%20were%20changing.%20There%20was%20an%20increasing%20demand%20for%20vegan%2C%20non-dairy%20alternatives%2C%