ents%20to%20cultivate.%20However%2C%20as%20I%20began%20to%20explore%20them%20further%2C%20I%20realised%20they%20are%20nutrient-dense%20and%20are%20considered%20a%20superfood%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Aditi%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Mali%20Greens%2C%20a%20business%20that%20offers%20over%2018%20different%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20to%20more%20than%20900%20customers%20across%20the%20city.%20We%20talked%20to%20her%20extensively%20about%20the%20intricacies%20of%20running%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304873%2Fkerala-man-grows-microgreens-superfood-at-home-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrogreens%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20you%20can%20start%20one%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Entrepreneurship%20is%20in%20my%20blood%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Aditi%20says%20that%20she%20has%20been%20learning%20and%20doing%20marketing%20for%20her%20father%20since%20she%20was%20a%20child.%20%E2%80%9CBusiness%20is%20in%20my%20blood.%20I%20have%20been%20around%20businessmen%20my%20whole%20life.%20However%2C%20as%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20started%20to%20drift%20a%20little%20towards%20other%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20graduation%2C%20she%20opted%20for%20Urban%20Planning%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20way%20villages%20work.%20%E2%80%9CI%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20rural%20lifestyle.%20The%20city%20life%20is%20good%20but%20if%20I%20was%20given%20a%20choice%2C%20I%20would%20have%20lived%20in%20a%20smaller%20city%20or%20farming%20in%20a%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20love%20was%20nurtured%20over%20time%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20study%20urban%20farming%20and%20nutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C