%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20SHIS%20Foundation%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20the%20patient%20numbers%20began%20to%20surge%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20peak%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20challenge%20of%20switching%20gears%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20French%20writer%2C%20Dominique%20Lapierre%2C%20was%20documenting%20the%20life%20of%20Gaston%20for%20his%20upcoming%20novel.%20When%20Gaston%20relayed%20the%20story%20of%20Wohab%20and%20Pal%20and%20their%20work%20to%20Lapierre%2C%20he%20was%20impressed.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20looking%20at%20four%20fully-equipped%20boats%20and%20two%20mobile%20emergency%20ambulances%20%E2%80%94%20Lapierre%E2%80%99s%20gift%20to%20their%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20how%20the%20SHIS%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Boat%20Clinic%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%2043%20years%20have%20witnessed%20the%20couple%20extending%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F183217%2Fnayi-disha-community-parents-children-special-needs-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20reach%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20including%20many%20programmes%20under%20its%20ambit.%20These%20include%20a%20tuberculosis%20control%20programme%2C%20an%20eye%20care%20hospital%2C%20a%20school%20for%20girls%2C%20a%20centre%20for%20disabled%20children%20to%20learn%2C%20and%20skill%20development%20programmes%20for%20the%20women%20of%20the%20Sundarbans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20clinic%20that%20comes%20to%20your%20doorstep%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Alam%20elaborates%20on%20the%20joys%20of%20this%20unique%20work%20setup%3B%20even%20as%